;&#10;Pyroblast: Hurl a massive fireball to the target inflicting 50 extra damage.   (Mana cost 15)&#10;&#10;Dragon Breath: Emit a fire breath just like a dragon , inflicting 15 extra damage to a target and Stunning him.   (Mana cost: 25)&#10;&#10;Flamestrike: Call down a column of fire upon a number of targets up to 4, inflicting 40 extra damage to all of them.   (Mana cost: 50)&#10;&#10;Holy Nova: Erupt with holy light inflicting 20 extra damage up to 4 targets.   (Mana cost: 25)&#10;&#10;Radiance:  Emanate holy light healing up to 4 targerts for 35% of their current health.   (Mana cost: 40)&#10;&#10;Chastise: Punish the target for his sins Stunning him.   (Mana cost: 20)&#10;&#10;Trueshot: Concentrate the targets aim increasing his physical critical damage by 25% for 5 rounds.   (Mana cost: 20)&#10;&#10;Bear Trap: Ensnare the target within a bear trap Freezing him.   (Mana cost: 15)&#10;&#10;Nature Wrath: Strike the target with the force of nature inflicting 30 extra damage.   (Mana cost: 15)&#10;&#10;Benefic Sporse: Shower up to 4 targets with healing spores healing them for 30 extra health points and causing them to Regenerate.   (Mana cost: 40)&#10;&#10;Antidote: Administer a powerful antidote to the target removing any active Poisons.   (Mana cost: 15)&#10;&#10;Entangling Roots: Entangle the target in overgrown roots Freezing them in place.   (Mana cost: 15)&#10;&#10;Duelist Step: Increase the target's reflexes increasing his physical defence for 3 roundsand his speed for 2 rounds.   (Mana cost: 30)" wrapText="true">
